Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you really need\Nto go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more minutes, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting to\Nthe really good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mane-iac is about to--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mane-iac?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Power Ponies'\Nmost evil nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the power-mad owner\Nof a hair-care product company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A tragic accident at her shampoo\Nfactory in Maretropolis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,not only gave her mane\Nstrange new powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but also caused her to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...completely insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She and her henchponies\Nare planning to break into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Maretropolis Museum\Nand steal the Electro-Orb
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so she can use it to power\Nup her doomsday device.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Mane-iac\Nwouldn't have even known
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if Hum Drum hadn't slipped\Nup and told her all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum Drum?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy in the blue boots\Nand pointless red cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Power Ponies' bumbling\Nand totally useless side-kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Power Ponies have\Nto stop the Mane-iac
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or Mare-tropolis is doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, Spike, if anypony\Nunderstands what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to get caught up in a\Nreally good book, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're going to make\Nany progress fixing up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna and Celestia's old\Ncastle tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we all have to\Ndo our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to be too\Ntired to lend a hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. OK. I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this magical\Nmake-over moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good ol' Spike is here\Nready to do his part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the other left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! That's perfect\Nright where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On to the next painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't\Nneed any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naw. That's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got everything\Nunder control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything\NI can help you with, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it\NSpike; it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've\Ngot it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking great, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you find a quiet spot\Nand finish reading your comic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you right at the part
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,where Hum Drum was about\Nto stop the villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum Drum never\Nstops the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just there\Nfor comic relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, let me give\Nyou a hoof with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's OK, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pony Power!{\i0}\N{\i1}Wheeee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mane-iac breaks\Ninto the museum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise, Hum\NDrum is in the way again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,while the Power Ponies\Ndo all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I know what\Nthat feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How can\Nthat be the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can retry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You can return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I saw a magnifying\Nglass lying around
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike! Where are ya,{\i0}\N{\i1}Spike!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're breaking for{\i0}\N{\i1}tea and biscuits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can return to the\Nplace you started
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Mane-iac\Nis defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...to join the\Nadventure in this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! What are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Maretropolis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somepony wanna tell{\i0}\N{\i1}me what the hay is going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy new\Npersonas, ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the Masked Matter-Horn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fili-Second.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zapp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}R... Radiance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mistress Mare-velous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saddle Rager.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Power Ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just call\Nus "Power Ponies"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the superheroes\Nfrom my comic book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It somehow zapped\Nus all in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So somepony zap us\Nback out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My comic book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It said the way to get\Nback to where we started
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was to defeat the Mane-iac.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arch-nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the mane event!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pinkie! Where'd she go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheeeeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be miles\Naway from here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie is Filli-Second,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the fastest pony in\Nall of Maretropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, freeze her mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Masked Matter-horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can shoot all kinds of crazy\Npower beams from your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm beginning\Nto enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Zapp and your\Nsuper-power is controlling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the mighty forces of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unholster the lightning bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning! Not a tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you're Saddle Rager!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose your temper\Nand you'll turn into a huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,super-strong monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Gosh. That wouldn't\Nbe very polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, use your jewelry\Nto create attack constructs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's an attack construct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think of\Nsomething... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and your bracelet\Nmakes it appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Electro-Orb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this has been quite the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,mane-raising experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really must be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you, Hum Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hum Drum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! You gotta\Nhelp stop the tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from destroying the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time I move, this\Ndarn lasso gets tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're psychically\Nconnected to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it to where you\Nwant it to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and it'll obey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, That was spintastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been sucked\Ninto some kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,comic book world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically,\Nit's called Maretropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we want to get\Nback to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have to\Nstop the Mane-iac
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from using her doomsday\Ndevice to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No biggie. I was\Nalready awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we've all\Ngot super powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all of us\Nhave super powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must have\Nthem too, Spikey-boo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,your character is\Nwearing a cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. For absolutely\Nno reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you're not\Nreally Hum Drum then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So the six of us "Power Ponies"\Nwill take care of Mane-iac
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and get us back to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, where is the Mane-iac\Nbuilding her doomsday device?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Her top secret headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'd better\Nget there quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That glowing orb she just stole\Nis what she's going to use
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to power it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a... shampoo factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Power Ponies,\Nhere's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you, me and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on out,{\i0}\N{\i1}Mane-iac!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Power Ponies\Nare coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for\Nelement of surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just hang back\Nhere doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think{\i0}\N{\i1}she's home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just\Ncome back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to "Power Pony Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh. Nice catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an improvement, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee hee! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I do so love a\Nfunctional accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't even just a\Nlittle angry right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice work,{\i0}\N{\i1}Power Ponies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's take care of the\NMane-iac and get ourselves home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a city to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not about to let\Nthe Power Ponies stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hair Spray Ray of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It stops you in your tracks\Nand renders your powers useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not so much\Nangry as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,bordering on terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hum Drum, why in\Nall of Mare-tropolis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would I use the Hair\NSpray Ray of Doom on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather pointless,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I supposed{\i0}\N{\i1}to do? I'm useless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder my friends never need\N{\i1}me to do anything important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're the ones with{\i0}\N{\i1}the super powers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They've probably already\Nfigured out how to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Power Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall live just long\Nenough to see me fire ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the instrument of\Nyour destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Electro-Orb\Nhas powered it up completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,this cannon will amplify\Nthe power of my mane
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,one million times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}expelling an energy blast{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that will cause everypony{\i0}\N{\i1}in Mare-tropolis' mane{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to grow wild!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be my weapon's\Nfirst victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and there is nopony who can{\i0}\N{\i1}save you from this fate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to interrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but aren't you forgetting\Nabout somepony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum Drum? Little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No superpowers whatsoever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's utterly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Everypony knows you\Njust keep him around
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because you feel\Nsorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But in our world\NSpike- uh, Hum Drum,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,always comes through\Nwhen we need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like Hum Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When my friends really\Nneed me, I do come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And they need me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see dementia\Nmust be a side-effect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of prolonged exposure to\Nthe Hair Spray Ray of Doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight we stand upon the\Nbrink of immortality,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for we collectively -\Nthough mostly me -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have finally defeated our{\i0}\N{\i1}most hated nemeses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have hurled the{\i0}\N{\i1}brush of badness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,into the now fearful face of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}goodness, and have struck{\i0}\N{\i1}a blow for freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the name of oppression!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing will stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tag! You're it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tag! You're it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tag! You're it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tag! You're it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There, THERE! IDIOTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Need a place to put these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have\Neverything under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, we need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to power up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that nothing\Nis making me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know you're evil\Nand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd hurt a teensy, little\Nharmless fire fly? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}WHY, YOU'RE JUST A{\i0}\N{\i1}GREAT BIG... MEANIE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE, I SAID IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT MAKES YOU THINK\NYOU'RE SO SPECIAL?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,LIKE THE RULES OF COMMON\NCOURTESY DON'T APPLY TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T YOU PICK\NON SOMEBODY YOUR OWN SIZE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, the\Nday is saved by--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see how I was raining\Ndown a storm of justice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You catch how I was\Nwieldin' that lasso?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a good half-second before\Nwe got sucked back out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of the comic and The\NMare-tropolis bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was only 65 blocks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't have made\Nit without you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that just because we don't\Nalways need your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean that we\Ndon't think you're helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you don't have\Nto have super powers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a super friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly did you\Nget that comic book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one I got in Canterlot at\NThe House of Enchanted Comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't know it meant\Nthey were literally enchanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it just meant like,\Nthe comics they sold there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,had really enchanting\Nstory lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait up! I'm an important\Npart of this team; remember?
